## Sequencing and Dependencies

The changes must be implemented in this order to avoid broken intermediate states:

1. **`useRocketMode.js` constants and refs** (Step 1 + 2) — foundation, nothing depends on old names externally
2. **`useRocketMode.js` helper function** (Step 3) — pure function, no dependencies
3. **`useRocketMode.js` `enter()`** (Step 4) — requires Step 1-3
4. **`useRocketMode.js` `exit()`** (Step 5) — requires Step 2 rename
5. **`useRocketMode.js` `sortStars()`** (Step 7) — requires `star.viewZ` field exists, set up in Step 4
6. **`useRocketMode.js` `tick()`** (Step 6) — requires Steps 1-5
7. **`useRocketMode.js` `project()`** (Step 8) — requires `star._rotX1` caching from Step 6
8. **`RocketLayer.jsx`** (Step 9) — requires Steps 1-8 complete; `project()` now returns null
9. **`RocketHUD.jsx`** (Step 10) — can be done in parallel with Steps 4-8, only depends on the ref rename
10. **`Universe.module.css`** (Step 11) — can be done any time

