## Summary of All File Changes

**`useRocketMode.js`** — Full rewrite of constants, refs, `enter()`, `exit()`, `tick()`, `sortStars()`, `project()`. Add `getForwardVector()` helper. Export `ROCKET_LABEL_Z_MAX`. Total line count increases by ~30 lines.

**`RocketLayer.jsx`** — Modify `sceneFunc` only: handle null from `project()`, replace outward speed lines with converging streaks, add label rendering pass after star draw. Import `ROCKET_LABEL_Z_MAX`. No changes to JSX structure. `focalLength` constant added at sceneFunc scope.

**`RocketHUD.jsx`** — Add `pitch` state, poll `rocketMode.pitch.current`, add pitch indicator element, update controls hint text. Add `useState` for pitch. Minor render change.

